<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Mix Fruits | REDMARVEL INTERNATIONAL</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mix-fruits.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Include Navbar -->
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <h1>Mix Fruits</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="fruit-description">
      <p>
        Indulge your senses with our premium selection of farm-fresh fruits, carefully sourced from the most fertile regions to ensure exceptional taste, texture, and quality. From the crisp sweetness of apples and the luscious richness of Valsadi mangoes to the creamy delight of bananas and the ruby-red burst of pomegranates, each fruit in our collection brings a unique and vibrant flavor experience. Add to that the zesty brightness of lemons and the juicy versatility of tomatoes, and you have a diverse range of nature’s finest offerings—perfect for snacking, cooking, or elevating any culinary creation with freshness and nourishment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <h1>Explore our offerings below</h1>
  </div>

  <!-- Product Sections -->

  <div class="section">
    <div class="image-container right">
      <img src="/image/fruits/original.jpg" alt="Apple">
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2>Apple</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Crisp and juicy fruit with a sweet-tart flavor, available in various varieties such as Fuji, Gala, and Granny Smith.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong> 10Kg Net</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Competitive pricing based on variety and size.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2> Valsadi Mango (Kesar, Alphanso, Rajapuri, Daseri)</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>  Luscious mangoes with rich, sweet flavors and smooth textures, each variety offering a unique taste experience.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong>  5Kg and 10Kg Boxes</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Prices vary by variety and seasonality, offering competitive rates for premium quality mangoes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/image/fruits/mango2.avif" alt="Mango">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="image-container right">
      <img src="/image/fruits/banana2.jpg" alt="Banana">
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2>Banana</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Creamy and sweet fruit with a soft texture, perfect for snacking, baking, or blending into smoothies.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong> 13Kg Net, 14Kg Gross Hands 4-5-6</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong>  Affordable pricing per dozen or per kilogram.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2> Pomegranate</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>  Ruby-red arils packed with juicy sweetness and tartness, versatile for use in salads, desserts, or as a refreshing snack</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong> 2Kg Net, 2.6Kg Gross ( Premium Quality).</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong>  Competitive rates per unit or per kilogram.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/image/fruits/pomegranate.webp" alt="Pomegranate">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="image-container right">
      <img src="/image/fruits/lemons.jpg" alt="Lemons">
    </div>
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2>Lemons</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> Tangy citrus fruits with bright yellow skins, essential for adding acidity and flavor to dishes, beverages, and sauces.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong>  6.5Kg Net, 7.2Kg Gross</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> Reasonably priced per dozen or per kilogram.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="text-container">
      <h2> Tomato</h2>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong>  Juicy and flavorful fruits with a versatile culinary profile, suitable for salads, sauces, soups, and more.</p>
      <p><strong>Packaging:</strong> Available in bulk crates or pre-packaged for retail sale</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong>  Competitive rates per unit or per kilogram.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/image/fruits/tomoto.jpg" alt="Tomato">
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
